message.body: Hey cuz! Hope all is well. Can I please get your new address???

Thanks so much. Everything has been good. Planning moms birthday and getting ready for number 3, and in a wedding......ahhhh so much. I miss you so much. You and hunter are more then welcome to stay here if you guys come for moms birthday weekend. The room has a private bath! :-)
Also, what is hunters last name?

Ok awesome. Wow... You are so busy to. Look mom wanted a small family gathering and well Danielle and I've changed it. Hahaha. So maybe it would've good not to get some things changed. I'm just kidding, it wouldn't be a real family event without some damn drama.
Hahaha. Seriously! It wouldn't feel right without the drama! Lol
It's gonna be a raging party!
It's an 80's party
Hahahaha. We are taking her back to her "favorite" decade.
The one she is still stuck in. Hahaha.
Hot neon colors and all.
Omg. Amazing.
Ahahahahahahajaja!!!!!
Soooo good!
Yeah. Should be fun.
Sounds like a blast! Are you guys settled in the house? All painted and everything?
We are about 75% in. Mom and dad are coming to help me in the baby's room on Saturday. The main level is good. All painted and organized.
That's so awesome! I'm glad you guys are in!
Thanks. How are you doing? How are you adjusting?

Really good! It's been super fun so far. Just seems natural. I was so nervous but it's been so easy to live together. I have been traveling a lot this past month so things might change now that I'm staying put for awhile
That's awesome. I'm sooooo glad to hear that.
Yeah I'm glad too! And the cats aren't killing each other! Well I'm about to get into bed but Send my love to Cesar and the boys! Luv ya cuz!
Yay. Sounds good. Love to both!
